					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/euro/" rel="category tag">Euro</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/europe/" rel="category tag">Europe</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/fiat-currency/" rel="category tag">Fiat currency</a></span>
